\lim _ {r\to 0}\frac {\sin (r^ 2 )}{r^2}=\frac {0}{0}
\lim _ {r\to 0}\frac {\sin (r^ 2 )}{r^2}=\lim _ {r\to 0}\frac {2r\cos(r^ 2 )}{2r}=\lim _ {r\to 0}\cos(r^ 2 )=1 
